.NET Core 1.0.name: DiscordClient
.NET Core 1.0.summary: The main interface with the Discord API.

methods.name: Connect(string token)
methods.summary: Attempts to connect to the Discord API with the token of the user/bot to authenticate as.
methods.returns: Returns whether or not the client successfully connected.

params.value: The token of the user/bot to authenticate as.

methods.name: Disconnect()
methods.summary: Disconnects this client from the Discord API.

methods.name: TryGetChannel(string id, DiscordChannel& channel)
methods.summary: Attempts to get a DiscordChannel by its id.
methods.returns: Returns whether or not the DiscordChannel was found.
methods.syntax: public bool TryGetChannel(string id, DiscordChannel& channel)
methods.linkedSyntax: public bool TryGetChannel(string id, DiscordChannel& channel)

methods.name: TryGetDirectMessageChannel(string id, DiscordDMChannel& dmChannel)
methods.summary: Attempts to get a DiscordDMChannel by its id.
methods.returns: Returns whether or not the DiscordDMChannel was found.
methods.syntax: public bool TryGetDirectMessageChannel(string id, DiscordDMChannel& dmChannel)
methods.linkedSyntax: public bool TryGetDirectMessageChannel(string id, DiscordDMChannel& dmChannel)

methods.name: TryGetGuild(string id, DiscordGuild& guild)
methods.summary: Attempts to get a DiscordGuild by its id.
methods.returns: Returns whether or not the DiscordGuild was found.
methods.syntax: public bool TryGetGuild(string id, DiscordGuild& guild)
methods.linkedSyntax: public bool TryGetGuild(string id, DiscordGuild& guild)

methods.name: TryGetUser(string id, DiscordUser& user)
methods.summary: Attempts to get a DiscordUser by their id.
methods.returns: Returns whether or not the DiscordUser was found.
methods.syntax: public bool TryGetUser(string id, DiscordUser& user)
methods.linkedSyntax: public bool TryGetUser(string id, DiscordUser& user)

methods.name: TryGetVoiceClient(DiscordGuild guild, DiscordVoiceClient& voiceClient)
methods.summary: Attempts to get a DiscordVoiceClient by the DiscordGuild it is in.
methods.returns: Returns where or not the DiscordVoiceClient was found.
methods.syntax: public bool TryGetVoiceClient(DiscordGuild guild, DiscordVoiceClient& voiceClient)

methods.name: UpdateStatus(string game, DiscordGameType gameType, Nullable<int> idleSince)
methods.summary: Updates the status of the currently authenticated user.

params.value: The type of game currently being played.
The time in seconds the user has been idle.

methods.syntax: public void UpdateStatus(string game, DiscordGameType gameType, Nullable<int> idleSince)
methods.linkedSyntax: public void UpdateStatus(string game, [DiscordGameType](#!type/Discore.DiscordGameType) gameType, Nullable<int> idleSince)

events.name: OnConnected
events.summary: Called when this client connects to the Discord API.

events.name: OnError
events.summary: Called when an error occurs in this client.

events.name: OnGuildBanAdd
events.summary: Called when a DiscordUser is banned from a DiscordGuild.

events.name: OnGuildBanRemove
events.summary: Called when a DiscordUser is unbanned from a DiscordGuild.

events.name: OnGuildEmojisUpdated
events.summary: Called the the DiscordEmojis of a DiscordGuild are updated.

events.name: OnGuildIntegrationsUpdated
events.summary: Called when an DiscordIntegration of a DiscordGuild is updated.

events.name: OnGuildMemberRemoved
events.summary: Called when a DiscordUser leaves or is removed from a DiscordGuild.

events.name: OnVoiceClientConnected
events.summary: Called when a voice connection is established.

events.name: OnVoiceClientDisconnected
events.summary: Called when a voice connection is terminated.

properties.name: Gateway
properties.summary: Gets the Discord gateway interface used by this DiscordClient.

properties.name: IsConnected
properties.summary: Gets whether or not this DiscordClient is connected to the Discord API.

properties.name: Rest
properties.summary: Gets the Discord REST interface used by this DiscordClient.
